  </div>
  <div class="steps">
    <div class="step reveal"><div class="step-num">01</div><div class="step-content"><h3>Free Consultation</h3><p>We learn about your goals, family, and concerns. No obligation, no pressure — just clarity.</p></div></div>
    <div class="step reveal reveal-d1"><div class="step-num">02</div><div class="step-content"><h3>Custom Plan Design</h3><p>We design a tailored estate plan that addresses your specific needs and situation.</p></div></div>
